--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README : BAMTOOLS, MODIFIED FOR USE BY LIBINORM
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a slight modification of the Bamtools library for use by LiBiNorm.

BamTools provides both a programmer's API and an end-user's toolkit for handling
BAM files.

I.   Learn More

II.  License

III. Acknowledgements

IV.  Contact

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
I. Learn More:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This version of Bamtools is based on bamtools 2.4.1 and has been modified for use by LiBiNorm

Modifications are:
	a)  A small number of changes to allow building by the Microsoft Visual C++ compiler
		as well as by gcc

	b)  Changes to reader::GetNextAlignment to allow decoding of just the tag data and not
		the other ascii data to improve efficiency

More information on the original bamtools software is available 
through the BamTools project wiki:

https://github.com/pezmaster31/bamtools/wiki


